<p>in 2018,BENGALLERY has now moved to the Blue House in Baiyun District . The Blue House is the only art gallery by the side of mother river in Guangzhou.</p>
<p>It's invested with multicultural mission to sail to international art sea....</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201129/c8e944aa3b4348f3996c4aceeb48f9ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>第25届秋季广州艺博会将于12月3日至6日在广州市海珠区新港东路630-638号南丰国际会展中心举行。据悉，BEN廊将携名家精品佳作亮相第25届秋季广州艺博会，欢迎大家前来观展。</p>
<p><strong>展览时间：</strong>12月3日至6日</p>
